T*
(3. Methodology) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.1 OBJ Import) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The BGR creation notebook is:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(classfications/S06-13A GML Creating BGR Graph - dan.ipynb) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The setup cell locates the OBJ folder automatically using candidate paths, so) Tj
T*
(the notebook can run from the repository root or from the notebook directory.) Tj
T*
(The OBJ files are imported with Topology.ByOBJPath:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(ground_objs = Topology.ByOBJPath\(str\(SUPPORT_DIR / "ground.obj"\), transposeAxes=False\)) Tj
T*
(column_objs = Topology.ByOBJPath\(str\(SUPPORT_DIR / "columns.obj"\), transposeAxes=False\)) Tj
T*
(office_objs = Topology.ByOBJPath\(str\(SUPPORT_DIR / "offices.obj"\), transposeAxes=False\)) Tj
T*
(core_objs = Topology.ByOBJPath\(str\(SUPPORT_DIR / "core.obj"\), transposeAxes=False\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.2 Semantic Cell Creation) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(For each imported object group, faces are extracted, flattened, self-merged,) Tj
T*
(and converted into cells. Each cell receives a dictionary containing:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- cell_type) Tj
T*
(- cell_name) Tj
T*
(- cell_color) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
