T*
(3.3 CellComplex and Dictionary Transfer) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The cells are merged into one CellComplex:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(model = Topology.SelfMerge\(Cluster.ByTopologies\(all_cells\)\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Dictionaries are transferred from internal selector vertices back to the cells:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(model = Topology.TransferDictionariesBySelectors\() Tj
T*
(    model,) Tj
T*
(    selectors,) Tj
T*
(    tranCells=True,) Tj
T*
(\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This step is important because the later graph vertices inherit semantic) Tj
T*
(information from the cells.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.4 Graph Construction and Feature Engineering) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The adjacency graph is created from the merged topology:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(graph = Graph.ByTopology\(model\)) Tj
T*
(vertices = Graph.Vertices\(graph\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Each vertex receives a one-hot encoding of its cell_type:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Feature | Meaning) Tj
T*
(feature_00 | ground) Tj
T*
(feature_01 | column) Tj
T*
(feature_02 | plinth / unused class) Tj
T*
(feature_03 | office) Tj
T*
(feature_04 | core) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The graph is exported to CSV using Graph.ExportToCSV.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
