T*
(Validation accuracy | 1.0000) Tj
T*
(Test accuracy | 1.0000) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(These metrics should be interpreted carefully. The dataset is very small and) Tj
T*
(imbalanced, and the validation and test masks cannot contain the rare ground) Tj
T*
(and core classes. Therefore, the result demonstrates a working pipeline rather) Tj
T*
(than a generalisable classifier.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7. Discussion) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The BGR workflow was successful. The assignment produced a valid topological) Tj
T*
(model, transferred semantic categories to cells, generated an adjacency graph,) Tj
T*
(and exported the dataset to CSV. The key modelling issue was not export) Tj
T*
(failure, but task selection. A single building graph cannot train a graph-level) Tj
T*
(classifier because graph classification learns from differences between many) Tj
T*
(graphs. The available data is more naturally suited to node classification,) Tj
T*
(because the single graph contains 55 labelled elements.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The node classification workflow demonstrates how graph machine learning can) Tj
T*
(be applied even when only one building is available. Each node represents a) Tj
T*
(semantic building component, and the graph structure describes adjacency) Tj
T*
(between components. However, a more robust experiment would require either:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- more buildings for graph classification, or) Tj
T*
(- more labelled nodes and more balanced categories for node classification.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(8. Conclusion) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This assignment converts layered architectural OBJ geometry into a Building) Tj
T*
(Graph Representation and uses it for graph machine learning. The generated BGR) Tj
T*
(contains one graph, 55 nodes, and 286 directed edge records. Since only one) Tj
T*
(graph is available, the workflow is adapted from graph classification to node) Tj
T*
(classification. A second dataset is generated with corrected node labels and) Tj
T*
(normalised coordinate features, and a GraphSAGE model is trained and saved.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The final deliverables demonstrate the complete pipeline:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Rhino OBJ geometry import.) Tj
T*
(2. Semantic cell labelling.) Tj
T*
(3. TopologicPy CellComplex creation.) Tj
T*
(4. BGR graph export.) Tj
T*
(5. Node classification dataset preparation.) Tj
T*
